Interface BinaryRelation<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the generic type of objects/pairs in this binary relation
    All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<net.sf.tweety.commons.util.Triple<T,T,Relation>>, Iterable<net.sf.tweety.commons.util.Triple<T,T,Relation>>, Set<net.sf.tweety.commons.util.Triple<T,T,Relation>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PreferenceOrder

    public interface BinaryRelation<T>
extends Set<net.sf.tweety.commons.util.Triple<T,T,Relation>>
    This abstract class provides a basic implementation of a generic set of pairs to be used for preference ordering.
    Author:
    Bastian Wolf
